description: This file contains declarations for ASN.1 object creation functions related to private key information and associated cryptographic structures. It appears to be part of a cryptography or ASN.1 handling library, defining interfaces for creating various ASN.1 structures such as PrivateKeyInfo, EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo, and specific key types like RSA and DSA.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateEncryptedPrivateKeyInfo
methods.description: Factory function to create an EncryptedPrivateKeyInfo ASN.1 object.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateEncryptionAlgorithmIdentifier
methods.description: Factory function to create an EncryptionAlgorithmIdentifier ASN.1 object.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreatePrivateKeyInfo
methods.description: Factory function to create a PrivateKeyInfo ASN.1 object.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreatePrivateKeyInfoWithKey
methods.description: Factory function to create a PrivateKeyInfo ASN.1 object with specific key type and parameters.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreatePrivateKey
methods.description: Factory function to create a private key ASN.1 object, either RSA or DSA.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateRSAPrivateKey
methods.description: Factory function to create an RSA private key ASN.1 object.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateDSAPrivateKey
methods.description: Factory function to create a DSA private key ASN.1 object.
